    <sec id="s1">
      <title>Introduction</title>
      <p>Biomedical literature is distributed as JATS XML by PubMed Central.
      This paragraph references <xref ref-type="bibr" rid="B1">Curie et al.</xref>
      and a figure <xref ref-type="fig" rid="f1">Figure 1</xref>.</p>
      <p>An <bold>emphasised</bold> clause with an <unknown-inline-tag>unmapped
      inline element</unknown-inline-tag> that must degrade to its child text.</p>
    </sec>
